# Believer's Gathering Place - Brand Typography Guide

This document defines all typography styles used across the BGP website to ensure brand consistency.

## Font Families

### Primary Font (Serif)
**Noto Serif** - Used for body text, quotes, and readable content

```css
--font-family-primary: 'Noto Serif', Georgia, serif;
```

**Google Fonts Import:**
```css
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif:wght@300;400;500&display=swap');
```

**Available Weights:**
- Light (300)
- Regular (400)
- Medium (500)

### Secondary Font (Sans-Serif)
**Montserrat** - Used for headings, navigation, and UI elements

```css
--font-family-secondary: 'Montserrat', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
```

**Google Fonts Import:**
```css
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@100;200;300;400;500&display=swap');
```

**Available Weights:**
- Thin (100)
- Extra Light (200)
- Light (300)
- Regular (400)
- Medium (500)

---

## Typography Scale

### Display Headings (Hero/Large)

| Element | Font Family | Size | Weight | Line Height | Letter Spacing |
|---------|-------------|------|--------|-------------|----------------|
| **Hero Title** | Montserrat | `clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem)` | 200 | 1.3 | Normal |
| **Large Display** | Montserrat | `3.5rem` (56px) | 200 | 1.2 | -0.03em |
| **404 Number** | Montserrat | `8rem` (128px) | 900 | 1 | Normal |

### Headings (H1-H6)

#### H1 - Main Page Title
```css
font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem); /* 40-56px */
font-weight: 200;
line-height: 1.2;
letter-spacing: -0.02em;
```

#### H2 - Section Title
```css
font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 4vw, 2.25rem); /* 30-36px */
font-weight: 200;
line-height: 1.2;
```

**Alternative H2 (Privacy/Legal)**
```css
font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
font-size: 2.75rem; /* 44px */
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1.2;
```

#### H3 - Card/Component Title
```css
font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
font-size: 1.75rem; /* 28px */
font-weight: 200;
line-height: 1.2;
```

**Alternative H3 (Strong)**
```css
font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
font-size: 1.75rem; /* 28px */
font-weight: 600;
```

#### H4 - Subsection Heading
```css
font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
font-size: 1.5rem; /* 24px */
font-weight: 300-500;
```

#### H5 - Small Heading
```css
font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
font-size: 1.25rem; /* 20px */
font-weight: 600;
```

#### H6 - Smallest Heading
```css
font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
font-size: 1.1rem; /* 17.6px */
font-weight: 300-400;
```

---

## Body Text

### Standard Body Text
```css
font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
font-size: 1rem; /* 16px */
font-weight: 300-400;
line-height: 1.6;
color: var(--color-text-dark); /* #333333 */
```

### Large Body Text
```css
font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
font-size: 1.125rem; /* 18px */
line-height: 1.7;
```

### Small Body Text
```css
font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
font-size: 0.875rem; /* 14px */
line-height: 1.6;
```

### Extra Small Text
```css
font-size: 0.85rem; /* 13.6px */
line-height: 1.5;
```

---

## Special Text Styles

### Hero Pretitle (Eyebrow)
```css
font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
font-weight: 300;
color: var(--color-gold);
text-transform: uppercase;
letter-spacing: 2px;
text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
```

### Hero Subtitle
```css
font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
font-weight: 300;
line-height: 1.6;
color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
```

### Blockquote (Leader Quote)
```css
font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
font-size: 1.125rem; /* 18px */
font-weight: 300-400;
line-height: 1.7;
font-style: italic;
padding-left: 1.5rem;
border-left: 4px solid var(--color-teal-mid);
```

### Strong Paragraph
```css
font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif;
font-size: 1.05rem; /* 16.8px */
font-weight: 400;
line-height: 1.7;
letter-spacing: 0.02em;
```

